{
  "lyrics": [
    {
      "start": 0,
      "end": 15.8,
      "text": "Wrapped me in a bolt of lightning Send me on my way still smiling",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 15.8,
      "end": 20.72,
      "text": "Maybe that\u0027s the way I should go Straight into the mouth of the unknown",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 20.72,
      "end": 25.68,
      "text": "I left the spare key on the table I never really thought I\u0027d be able",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 25.919999999999998,
      "end": 30.08,
      "text": "Say I merely visit on the weekends I lost my whole life and a dear friend",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 30.08,
      "end": 39.72,
      "text": "I\u0027ve said it so many times I would change my ways, no, never mind",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 39.72,
      "end": 48.8,
      "text": "God knows I\u0027ve tried Call me a sinner, call me a saint",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 49.4,
      "end": 53.76,
      "text": "Tell me it\u0027s over, I\u0027ll still rob you the same",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 53.76,
      "end": 63.8,
      "text": "Call me your favorite, call me the worst Tell me it\u0027s over, I don\u0027t want you to hurt",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 63.8,
      "end": 72.47999999999999,
      "text": "It\u0027s all that I can say So I\u0027ll be on my way",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 78.8,
      "end": 86.96,
      "text": "I finally put it all together That nothing really lasts forever",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 86.96,
      "end": 92.56,
      "text": "I had to make a choice that was not mine I had to say goodbye for the last time",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 92.56,
      "end": 97.56,
      "text": "I kept my whole life in a suitcase Never really stayed in one place",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 97.56,
      "end": 102.47999999999999,
      "text": "Maybe that\u0027s the way it should be You know I live my life like a gypsy",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
